title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 2 categories of Country on the x axis representing 2 groups: Men, and Women.
Averaging the 2 groups, the highest category is found for Country 65 years with a mean value of 20.3.
The minimum category is found at 45 years with a mean value of 10.95.
In case of 65 years, Men shows more dominance than any other Country and it has the lowest value in 45 years.
